'''Welcome''' to the official VRChat Wiki!
This is a community-driven collaborative guide to [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]]. You can find, and contribute information about various topics consistent with VRChat, such as official VRChat content and features, or notable community-created worlds and avatars.

==About the VRChat Wiki==

The VRChat Wiki began construction in late May, 2024<ref>[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/vrc-official-wiki-discussion/24217 'VRC Official Wiki Discussion'] on ''ask.vrchat.com''; retrieved December 11, 2024.</ref>, originally using [https://www.dokuwiki.org/dokuwiki DokuWiki] as its foundation, but was later changed to [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/MediaWiki MediaWiki] software. Three months later, the VRCWiki was announced to the public on VRChat's August 22<ref>[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/developer-update-22-aug-2024/26325 'Developer Update' - 22 Aug 2024] on ''ask.vrchat.com''; retrieved December 11, 2024.</ref> [[Developer Update|developer update]].

If you are interested in contributing to the VRChat Wiki, please read our [[VRCWiki:How to Contribute]] guide, as well as the [[VRCWiki:Guidelines]] page. We would like to see what you can do to help improve the Wiki! You must log in with your [[VRChat Account|VRChat account]] before making changes. Also be sure to check out the [[Special:MyLanguage/VRCWiki:Contributor_portal|contributor portal]] for all the information on VRChat Wiki's rules, policies, and guidelines.

Be sure to join the [[Discord servers|VRChat Wiki Discord server]] to get in touch with other editors!

